{"tid":776220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺安全感緊要過自信","createTime":"2018-08-11T22:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T02:26:49.000Z","uid":58316,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c8fb203573031110f57adc2b018f71f00d3fab60","tid":776220,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T22:03:08.000Z","msg":"安全感同自信可唔可以並存？<br />\n唔知<br />\n老實講<br />\n即使我明自信點解<br />\n但我心目中自信呢樣野感覺上係d扮出黎既野<br />\n自信就做俾人睇<br />\n安全感就自己在心中<br />\n可能人人性格唔同<br />\n或者我呢份人註定成世揾安全感<br />\n可以係一個moment消失得無影無蹤<br />\n到揾返又會好窩心<br />\n失而復得，得而復失<br />\n好似我人生就係不斷捕捉安全感既旅程<br />\n試過無數次叫自己有自信<br />\n講野firm d<br />\n試過屈自己係某種人<br />\n好受歡迎好hyper好世界仔個種人<br />\n乜都一笑置之好瀟個種壞男人<br />\n但唔得囉<br />\n我永遠都係趁人唔為意<br />\n監察人一舉一動<br />\n凡事唔抵得眼紅人個種人<br />\n永遠都係咁冇自信<br />\n永遠都係咁驚被社會遺棄俾社會當垃圾一把火燒成灰<br />\neven我係垃圾<br />\n都想用呢幾廿年<br />\n享受埋人生僅餘既快樂<br />\n係垃圾堆中望住個世界轉<br />\n就算自己週身污糟邋塌<br />\n已經成為我既保護色<br />\n保護住我僅有但又可以隨時唔見既安全感"},{"pid":"052e94eda997748b8235fc3c5386132c6ec238a1","tid":776220,"uid":58316,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T22:08:51.000Z","msg":"上左十年高登連登<br />\n可以同你地講<br />\n上黎打d冇人睇既廢話<br />\n係我除左打j之外最正既享受<br />\n係出面扮到幾勁都好<br />\n一返到自己間房<br />\n卸下武裝<br />\n就露底<br />\n但亦都係最有安全感"},{"pid":"2f8e91ac7f5923cb40c4277e82b07edcd980f14d","tid":776220,"uid":58316,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T22:15:34.000Z","msg":"尋氣都要講多次<br />\n出面真係揾唔到安全感<br />\n份工幾好<br />\n事業有成<br />\n都掩飾唔到自己有幾驚<br />\n成日諗<br />\n點解社會咁鍾意以事業define人<br />\n唔理喇<br />\n如果社會因為咁而懲罰我<br />\n就算玩謝我<br />\n當人生行到最後<br />\n我都會咁自戀<br />\n世界曾經有一個人<br />\n係咁自戀過<br />\n咁錫自己"},{"pid":"8456bef2af14af3508ec9b34271cff645584c5ac","tid":776220,"uid":171598,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T22:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/061727_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F061727_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=0237343a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/061730_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F061730_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=dd5c0791&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"003508195d00684a81a96d1a448631c1fd5c43e1","tid":776220,"uid":26038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T22:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908a2cb2d176cfc3de0a712c354f6b1f078a6c2e","tid":776220,"uid":72847,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T22:40:00.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630092411bd105acf854127b3a3530c9765e6e70","tid":776220,"uid":184312,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T23:08:51.000Z","msg":"搞清楚 係你既自信先至係扮出黎"},{"pid":"f992ce9bd270f4a7ce3cf0b00d834d3da988aaee","tid":776220,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T01:23:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"690fd929253f9021c9c253beed9203b5235525a1","tid":776220,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f992ce9bd270f4a7ce3cf0b00d834d3da988aaee","tid":776220,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8456bef2af14af3508ec9b34271cff645584c5ac","tid":776220,"uid":171598,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T22:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/061727_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F061727_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=0237343a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/061730_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-t